  id: 32
  title: "Nh\u1EADt k\xFD h\xE0ng x\xF3m #15 \u2014 Ng\u01B0\u1EDDi m\u1EB9 \u1EDF
    t\u1EA7ng 8"
  category: 3
  content: "Con t\xF4i, b\xE9 Mia, \u0111\xE3 b\u1ECB c\u1EAFn h\xF4m qua. T\xF4i
    tr\xF3i n\xF3 v\xE0o gi\u01B0\u1EDDng. B\xE1c s\u0129 n\xF3i 6 gi\u1EDD l\xE0
    s\u1EBD bi\u1EBFn. \u0110\xE3 8 ti\u1EBFng r\u1ED3i m\xE0 n\xF3 v\u1EABn c\xF2n
    nh\u1EADn ra t\xF4i. N\xF3 g\u1ECDi 'm\u1EB9 \u01A1i' b\u1EB1ng gi\u1ECDng y\u1EBFu
    \u1EDBt. T\xF4i kh\xF4ng bi\u1EBFt ph\u1EA3i l\xE0m g\xEC. N\u1EBFu ai \u0111\u1ECDc
    \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c cu\u1ED1n n\xE0y, xin h\xE3y cho t\xF4i bi\u1EBFt \u2014
    c\xF3 c\xE1ch n\xE0o c\u1EE9u n\xF3 kh\xF4ng? T\xF4i nghe n\xF3i c\xF3 nghi\xEAn
    c\u1EE9u thu\u1ED1c gi\u1EA3i \u1EDF \u0111\xE2u \u0111\xF3. Xin h\xE3y..."
  image: {fileID: 0}
  voiceLog: {fileID: 0}
